{"id":232468930,"title":"#食譜  沙茶空心菜豬肉片","content":"晚安我是阿杰，好久沒有po自己煮的東西了，這禮拜回來臺中，就煮了這道菜。\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/apDVOBN.jpg\n\n\n#空心菜炒豬肉片\n#沙茶口味\n\n每次回到家，都會找時間煮個東西，因為在外面要煮真的不太容易，電費高、食材用具那些又沒有很齊全，家裡就不同了，因為媽媽平常有在煮，所以基本上東西都有，只要再去買個菜就好了。\n\n食材\n\n豬肉片 一大盒\n空心菜 一把\n蒜頭3-4顆\n辣椒 一根\n醃漬-----------\n米酒 一大匙\n醬油 一大匙\n\n沙茶醬 兩大匙\n\n作法\n\n1.豬肉片用米酒  醬油醃漬\n2.空心菜洗好切段 \n蒜頭切碎 辣椒切小段\n3.熱鍋  一匙沙茶醬跟蒜碎爆香\n4.下豬肉拌炒 加少許的米酒\n把豬肉炒到熟\n5.下空心菜 再一點米酒 空心菜炒軟之後 再下一匙沙茶醬拌一拌 \n6.試一下味道 撒上辣椒段\n就可以盛盤了\n\n更多的食譜跟日常小故事\n有空可以來看看哦\nhttps://m.facebook.com/cookRJ/?ref=bookmarks","excerpt":"晚安我是阿杰，好久沒有po自己煮的東西了，這禮拜回來臺中，就煮了這道菜。#空心菜炒豬肉片，#沙茶口味，每次回到家，都會找時間煮個東西，因為在外面要煮真的不太容易，電費高、食材用具那些又沒有很齊全，家裡","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d7db42a8-bedb-4ea2-96a7-c9034f4dd89a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-09T11:02:36.709Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-09T11:04:04.051Z","commentCount":7,"likeCount":31,"tags":[],"topics":["食譜","烹飪","懶人料理"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"烹飪","forumAlias":"cooking","school":"菜鳥廚師阿杰","department":"tonykey125","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":30},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/apDVOBN.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"8d9cba48-5c0a-42b5-8826-ad1054e15d47","url":"https://i.imgur.com/apDVOBNl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/apDVOBNl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/apDVOBNl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-09T11:02:36.709Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-09T11:04:04.051Z"},{"id":"8d9cba48-5c0a-42b5-8826-ad1054e15d47","url":"https://i.imgur.com/apDVOBN.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/apDVOBN","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/apDVOBNl.jpg"